its been over a year.idk. i try but no one seems to want to stick around =/. maybe everyone can just sense my fears of love and trust, i duno haha =p.

but honestly on that note. i guess i cant settle for someone who is just kind of eh with me. i want someone who enojys me. and will hang out with me and not make me feel like shit one day and awesome the next.
Please, don't be offended, but it's not that I miss you. It's that I miss feeling whole.

yah well summed up april vacation was really random for the most part. I didnt really do anything huge, but it was really fuun either way. 

Went to the beach, went out for ice cream, played a lil balllll, straight chilled, walk the line, fat chickened, burst out in freckles, went to the mall for the first time in months, got a staph infection... you know.

and now its like 7 and wide awake and have church in a couple hours and then breakfast and whatever for greek easter. fgnoi snti0rjht 920tr

i had fuuun last night.



but yaah, #$@@%%#^$^&%**($#%#@RVWERS ASdf s I dont know.

fuck this. haha im not meant for one of these. i cant figure out like anything and it gets me so stressed out aha.

but anyways.

yesterday i ran to chrissys like old times and we sat around and ate so much food (like old times.) and yah. then michelle came and we drove around and picked up people. i opened max up to tom petty and he loved him :). then i had to pee really bad so i just did my thing and was classy and peed in a cup in the callery dug out. :-/
then i went to kells because we dont bond enough anymore and i missed her. and two of her boys came over and we painted easter eggs. she asked about my love life. ah, yah kell forgot i dont have one.
i came home and went online and attempted good will hunting for the 2nd time and fell asleep and actually slept until 11 which is a record for me. went running and then showered and out to meghans game wuth feeley and amy. 
then kaylas lake house and barbequed then ice cream then here for walk the line which is actually really good.

ah, i dont even know.
i get to certain points with people when i just start pushing them away and i really dont like it.

and since im GREEK easter is next sunday, but i guess we're celebratiing it tomorrow which is weiirrrd. stinks cuz we used to go all out and roast the lamb but now my mom just buys the dinky lamb chops at market basket and ugh :-/. i need to sleep.

I hope you choke on every word you spoke when you were screaming at me. And realize how many times I've tried, but that's wishful thinking. All I want is an apology for what you did and how you treated me. Get me far away, or at least as far as this car will take me. Tell all your friends about me.
GOOD. thats all.

it happens. hm but anyways. I'm still trying to decide if today ended up being a good day or a bad one. Well not so much bad, just like ah.. mediocre. But i did "hang out" -if thats what you want to call it-with chrissy after practice. We didnt really do much just sit on the corner of fletcher street and call every person known to man with a car. Almost got like i dont even know. FINALLY GOT A RIDE. Chrissy tripped on the curb ahah and a drunk laughed at her aha but i miss hanging out with her so so much so its good, regardless of what we do and stuff.

mmkay, well I give 99.9% of the credit to chrissy for helping me with this - all i did was pick the lay out i liked, she did everything else. [thanks again pal!] I guess im just dumber than i thought with computers, but im excited ive wanted one of these for the longest time :-D!! aha, but anyways. I'm going to take complete advantage of this thing hah... I woke up kind of late for me [1030ish] and went online like usual, went running and then had softball practice which was goood, i ran around a lot and chrissy couldnt throw because of her pinky and i laughed so much because she threw kind of crooked. i think the sun kind of got to me though cuz i feel kind of tired but whatever. then i went home quick and planned on taking a shower, but didnt. ugh, and didnt go to tommy's show :( but hey i guess theres always next time [still sorry!!] but yeah so chrissy came and got me and we ate food and straight chilled and then around 7ish kell came over and we bonded a little. and then rich called around 730? and he picked us up and sorry rich but you kind of scare me with your driving. met up with kevin, and mike and ashley and went to this weird place and me and chrissy stayed in the car.. aha. and then went to dunkins then i came home and took a shower and attempted homework but had more important things to be doing :) i took so many pictures this weekend :) ah but i will for sure talk more tomorrow, paayce.
